</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:12
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='301894' id='t-301894'>I was flying on a trip,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='305013' id='t-305013'>and I was witness to an incident</span>
