<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='319029' id='t-319029'>He was yelled at for attempting to board</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='320875' id='t-320875'>one group too soon.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='323246' id='t-323246'>So I said something.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='324690' id='t-324690'>I said, &quot;Why do you have treat us like cattle?</span>
