<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='330451' id='t-330451'>And this is exactly what she said to me.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='332572' id='t-332572'>She said, &quot;Sir, if I don't follow the rules,</span>
