<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:06
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='355434' id='t-355434'>You see, if the conditions are wrong,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='357356' id='t-357356'>we are forced to expend our own time and energy</span>
