<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='362479' id='t-362479'>and that inherently weakens the organization.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='365778' id='t-365778'>When we feel safe inside the organization,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='367409' id='t-367409'>we will naturally combine our talents</span>
