<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='373431' id='t-373431'>and seize the opportunities.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:27
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='376566' id='t-376566'>The closest analogy I can give</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='377887' id='t-377887'>to what a great leader is, is like being a parent.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='381099' id='t-381099'>If you think about what being a great parent is,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='382758' id='t-382758'>what do you want? What makes a great parent?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='384588' id='t-384588'>We want to give our child opportunities,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='385940' id='t-385940'>education, discipline them when necessary,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='388658' id='t-388658'>all so that they can grow up and achieve more</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='390694' id='t-390694'>than we could for ourselves.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='393259' id='t-393259'>Great leaders want exactly the same thing.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='395000' id='t-395000'>They want to provide their people opportunity,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='396501' id='t-396501'>education, discipline when necessary,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='398288' id='t-398288'>build their self-confidence, give
them the opportunity to try and fail,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='401450' id='t-401450'>all so that they could achieve more</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='403161' id='t-403161'>than we could ever imagine for ourselves.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:58
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='407591' id='t-407591'>Charlie Kim, who's the CEO of
a company called Next Jump</span>
