<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='484966' id='t-484966'>None at all.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='486298' id='t-486298'>Great leaders would never sacrifice</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='488509' id='t-488509'>the people to save the numbers.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='489870' id='t-489870'>They would sooner sacrifice the numbers</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='491549' id='t-491549'>to save the people.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
