 8:25
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='494528' id='t-494528'>Bob Chapman, who runs</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='496651' id='t-496651'>a large manufacturing company in the Midwest</span>
