<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='516172' id='t-516172'>They needed to save 10 million dollars,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='517875' id='t-517875'>so, like so many companies today,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='519898' id='t-519898'>the board got together and discussed layoffs.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='523292' id='t-523292'>And Bob refused.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='524916' id='t-524916'>You see, Bob doesn't believe in head counts.</span>
