<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='553532' id='t-553532'>He said, it's better that we should all suffer a little</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='556180' id='t-556180'>than any of us should have to suffer a lot,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='558965' id='t-558965'>and morale went up.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='562083' id='t-562083'>They saved 20 million dollars,</span>
