<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='587080' id='t-587080'>Leadership is a choice. It is not a rank.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='590014' id='t-590014'>I know many people at the seniormost</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='591722' id='t-591722'>levels of organizations</span>
